{"tid":723950,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣都係嘆息我地呢個年代或者唔會有球王登基","createTime":"2018-06-30T16:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T17:19:12.000Z","uid":159144,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1add634faac19247b31790e1fe2be6f4f2187d4b","tid":723950,"uid":159144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"歷史上得3個人可以稱得上係球王<br />\n1. 比利<br />\n2. 老馬<br />\n3. 拖舟<br />\n<br />\n去到我地今個時代, 丙朗同美欺當然係分庭抗禮<br />\n做球王當然一定要拎過世界盃, <br />\n今次世界盃係佢地最後嘅機會登基成為球王<br />\n美欺下次再踢到世界盃都好, 個壯態都好難KEEP到近年顛峰, 所以基本上已經無可能登基<br />\n依家得返阿朗, 重有幾個鐘就知佢行唔行到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論真係覺得阿朗定美欺勁啲, 其實都好想見證我地今個年代真正有球王登基!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f22c858441d5a38bc0cf7c4182b3610871504ac","tid":723950,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"你當巴西3R死架 02年攞晒全世界既彩???"},{"pid":"3d3dc62ef0705ebfbb4d911e1633391668da3e32","tid":723950,"uid":171509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4f22c858441d5a38bc0cf7c4182b3610871504ac","tid":723950,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"你當巴西3R死架 02年攞晒全世界既彩???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"佢淨係識呢啲架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c758a2e4bb95506cab878470713ebc79f8f7b639","tid":723950,"uid":40839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:27:37.000Z","msg":"下個包皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77b74abbda59efa87d7eaa0caacfbe5ab6e6e31","tid":723950,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:27:45.000Z","msg":"朗拿癲奴都唔係球王？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af